OL,3,CFrance restricts public drinking and
OL,4,Coutdoor sports as heatwave hits Europe
OL,6,FFrance is putting emergency services
OL,7,Fand military forces on wildfire alert,
OL,8,Frestricting public alcohol consumption
OL,9,Fand cancelling some outdoor sports
OL,10,Fevents to cope with a heat wave
OL,11,Funfurling across parts of Europe.
OL,13,FAbout a third of France is under the
OL,14,Fnational weather service's heat red
OL,15,Falert on Sunday, and temperatures are
OL,16,Fhigh nationwide, expected to reach 40C
OL,17,Fon Sunday in some areas.
OL,19,FThe forecast for Monday is even hotter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
