FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782047474
OL,3,CFrance restricts public drinking and
OL,4,Coutdoor sports as heatwave hits Europe
OL,6,FThe government banned public drinking
OL,7,Fin ''red alert'' zones, and ordered
OL,8,Forganisers of music day events to
OL,9,Flimit alcohol use to "preserve
OL,10,Femergency services and allow medics to
OL,11,Fconcentrate on taking care of the most
OL,12,Fvulnerable."
OL,14,FMore above-average temperatures are
OL,15,Fexpected this summer, which can cause
OL,16,Fheat exhaustion and life-threatening
OL,17,Fheat stroke.
OL,26,@qD@VOUtD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
