OL,3,CFrance restricts public drinking and
OL,4,Coutdoor sports as heatwave hits Europe
OL,6,FIn the UK, the Met Office has issued
OL,7,Fan Amber extreme heat warning for most
OL,8,Fof southern England and the Midlands,
OL,9,Fand large swathes of Wales.
OL,11,FThe warning runs through Monday and
OL,12,FTuesday, as temperatures are forecast
OL,13,Fto reach as high as 35C.
OL,15,FIt highlights that those vulnerable to
OL,16,Fextreme heat could have their health
OL,17,Fimpacted, and the hot weather could
OL,18,Faffect sectors such as transport,
OL,19,Fenergy and water supplies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
