PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782047474
OL,3,CFrance restricts public drinking and
OL,4,Coutdoor sports as heatwave hits Europe
OL,6,FThere could also be an increase in
OL,7,Fwater safety incidents, as people are
OL,8,Fmore likely to flock to coastal areas,
OL,9,Fas well as rivers and lakes.
OL,11,FAt least 15 people died during water-
OL,12,Frelated incidents during the May
OL,13,Fheatwave, the majority of victims
OL,14,Fbeing teenagers.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
