PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782047474
OL,3,CFrance restricts public drinking and
OL,4,Coutdoor sports as heatwave hits Europe
OL,6,FIn Italy, authorities expanded heat
OL,7,Fwarnings, referred to locally as "red
OL,8,Fflags", from seven to eight cities for
OL,9,FSunday, in northern and central parts
OL,10,Fof the country.
OL,12,FAt one farm outside Milan, owners set
OL,13,Fup fans and sprinklers to keep cows
OL,14,Fcool. In Rome, tourists dunked their
OL,15,Farms and occasionally their faces into
OL,16,Fthe city's famed fountain pools.
